'Urban Dictionary' is a Web-based dictionary of slang words and phrases, which
contains 6,969,824 definitions . [http://www.urbandictionary.com/ Home
page] Submissions are regulated by volunteer editors and rated by site
visitors. [[Time (magazine)|Time]] 's Anita Hamilton included it
on her 50 best websites of 2008 list.
